<emphasis id="239AEAD5560C694FC8DC02ED8253F987" bold="true" box="[199,324,1521,1547]" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
Male as discussed under 
<taxonomicName id="D6EE4D44560C694FCA7302EE801AF987" authority="Li" authorityName="Li" authorityYear="2016" box="[616,781,1521,1547]" class="Insecta" family="Pyralidae" genus="Teliphasa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="erythrina">
